        "content": "\n    <div class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding: 40px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h2 style='margin-top:0;'>Vocal-Sync 広告イメージ</h2>\n        <p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">あなたの日常に、無意識の最適化を。</p>\n        <div style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); overflow: hidden;\">\n            <img src=\"images/広告イメージ.jpeg\" onclick=\"openModal(this.src)\" alt=\"Vocal-Sync 広告イメージ\" style=\"width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer;\">\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;\">メモ：日本語がおかしい部分があるので要修正。</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 画像拡大用モーダルコンテナ -->\n    <div id=\"imageModal\" onclick=\"closeModal()\" style=\"display: none; position: fixed; z-index: 9999; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: zoom-out;\">\n        <img id=\"modalImage\" style=\"max-width: 90%; max-height: 90%; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #555; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); object-fit: contain; cursor: default;\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();\">\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        function openModal(src) {\n            var modal = document.getElementById('imageModal');\n            var modalImg = document.getElementById('modalImage');\n            modal.style.display = \"flex\";\n            modalImg.src = src;\n        }\n        function closeModal() {\n            var modal = document.getElementById('imageModal');\n            var modalImg = document.getElementById('modalImage');\n            modal.style.display = \"none\";\n        }\n    </script>\n",
